{"tid":1481137,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鍾鎮濤再撐警：暴力係冇用","createTime":"2019-08-17T14:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T17:25:03.000Z","uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"9b7aabb055a04862b68c89d23d5af68ddc3f0b5e","tid":1481137,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190817/s00009/3b0a58d5cfa782e300860340559ad3a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190817%2Fs00009%2F3b0a58d5cfa782e300860340559ad3a2.jpg&h=4fe2cb04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鍾鎮濤（阿B）於6月底曾跟梁家輝及譚詠麟（阿倫）參加撐警集會，阿B當日罵年輕人「九唔搭八」，稱奉公守法是理所當然的事。事後有歌迷將阿B和阿倫的唱片毁掉，以示對他們的言論表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n今日阿B出席「反暴力 救香港」集會，同場還有鄺美雲和張明敏等圈中人，阿B又手持國旗拍照，阿B在台上表示，很高興見到沉默一群出來「反暴力 救香港」，他聲稱「支持警隊」，暴力沒有用，否則學校就不會取消體罰，他認為暴力會令社會有不良後果，甚至「令大家都無得撈」，阿B表示香港是大家土生土長的地方，沒人有權破壞，他希望更多演藝界人士出來。他續說：「無國不會有家。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/17/NCPY5q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F17%2FNCPY5q.png&h=20919263&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"823063360d6851fdb670d7b5bf28e12e1b164400","tid":1481137,"uid":207195,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"冇國不會有家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇牆不會有磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31904d43ff6d2eebc7221abc77c8a67e804896ba","tid":1481137,"uid":15605,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"破產濤"},{"pid":"334242b8c375cca7f1ca648e92a6c0b902a06045","tid":1481137,"uid":67813,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"元朗事件你又唔講，射爆眼你又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話band 友"},{"pid":"c02f6340ee06694fe85f7ca387e61966718bd813","tid